name: Failure to comply with court orders
text: [§346-246]  Failure to comply with court orders.  The court may apply contempt of court provisions and all other provisions available under the law if a party fails to comply with the terms and conditions of any order issued under this part. [L 1989, c 381, pt of §1; am L 1990, c 144, §1 and c 234, §9]
